{"word":"ἀυτέω","slug":"ἀυτέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀυτέω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>αὔω</el> <i>to cry</i>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>From <el>ἀύτη</el>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to cry, shout</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>:—<a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> cogn., <el>βοὰν ἀϋτῶ</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; <el>ἀϋτεῖ δ' ὀξύ</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a> <i>to call to</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>:—<a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a> et <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}